body:
Thank you very much, it was the comma. Values are high because of 99% glazing in the south.

By looking for the mistake (and not having seen the comma) I found the units within the first line of the *.csv-file [Date/Time,VF:Zone People Total Heating Energy [J](Hourly),VF:Zone Lights Electric Energy [J](Hourly),VF:Zone Electric Equipment Electric Energy [J](Hourly), etc.] Therefor I was mentioning the J-values.



Thanks Abraham and Mostapha,

D
